metadata.name: Sweet Nightmare #001
metadata.description:
# "Sweet Nightmare" various glitches by Hollow himself. 

 Glitch is "a problem or fault that prevents something from being successful or working as well as it should." But in this case, this kind of manipulation can definitely "improve" some of my hand-painted pieces.

It gives it a unique expression, style, and movement that I genuinely love, and that result is "impossible" to achieve without human-computer collaboration.
